{"tid":85490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同伯母講我做運輸 佢即刻收埋隻雞","createTime":"2017-01-18T11:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T11:45:41.000Z","uid":31739,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4272ea03ffe8b42df58360860a6680cfe51972e0","tid":85490,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊左兩年<br />\n尋晚就第一次上佢屋企食飯<br />\n上之前都淆淆地底 始終第一次<br />\n上到去 得伯母都係到 <br />\n我送左支貴紅酒 咁伯母就收左 笑笑口叫我唔好咁客氣<br />\n大家傾左兩句就埋枱食飯<br />\n一開始氣氛都ok嘅 有講有笑咁<br />\n食左兩啖就黎料<br />\n<br />\n伯母: 係呢 你係做邊行架?<br />\n我: Errrrrrr (我望一望女友 之後笑左一笑) 我係做運輸嘅<br />\n伯母: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻西臉 一粒聲都唔出<br />\n女友: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過左十幾秒嘅寂靜後<br />\n伯母: 我都係留番半隻雞聽日做餸 你唔介意架可<br />\n我: 唔... 唔介意<br />\n跟住佢就轉身拎走左碟雞入廚房<br />\n<br />\n跟著女友靠埋黎 細細聲講<br />\n女友: 喂叫左你唔好玩野架嘛<br />\n我: 我無諗過佢會咁大反應架嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n伯母呢刻行番出黎 繼續食飯<br />\n伯母: 咁係載客定載貨?<br />\n我: 我一出黎就多數載貨嘅 呢排岩岩轉左載客<br />\n女友: 媽 其實呢佢係做...... (被打斷)<br />\n伯母: (西面) 其實呢行載咩都係搵得唔多嘅<br />\n我: 都...都岩嘅 而且時間唔穩定 有時都幾危險架 <br />\n女友: 媽 其實呢佢係做...... (被打斷)<br />\n伯母: (西面) 咁你有無搵過轉工呀?<br />\n我: 暫時都應該唔諗啦 其...其實而家咁都仲過得去呀......<br />\n<br />\n女友: 玩夠未呀?!??! 媽 其實呢佢係做機師架! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 最後有番隻雞食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n伯母: 係呢 你係做"},{"pid":"b26978704a7121675eeae0796c8ca97491ca77c5","tid":85490,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"咁賤格架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飛咗你條女啦"},{"pid":"73d86ae8c875a78cc4b02b27f9eb67184d8e93fd","tid":85490,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"邊套戲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e48e584e8be13b1e0a032f82c2e8ba2a4be0edb","tid":85490,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"又番炒"},{"pid":"8e5059179ebabaa3628c1b2957f9b22a83aadcd5","tid":85490,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"打飛機師"},{"pid":"88508b90afbb16a36032e4a54aafa44f89d71020","tid":85490,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"有時都會ff自己有咁既一日"},{"pid":"7fbbdbc02b6e021f8772673114ab4a0d6078635a","tid":85490,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08ce166cdef53ab7cebb424f19a14577cb2e201","tid":85490,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:08:42.000Z","msg":"回帶？"},{"pid":"20295390b6321613228f2cdda712c8ba3a0bd871","tid":85490,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"伯母無啦啦做咩叫自己個女入房？"},{"pid":"75dc9eb44a3d134a26e3ad09569fc38f0eaca915","tid":85490,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:11:04.000Z","msg":"玩大左 唔知伯母以後會點睇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c02840185a209d3699a040eceefc3af7a2a133","tid":85490,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:18:22.000Z","msg":"Uncle 全程唔出聲？"},{"pid":"e7c0d0ad01c31605e01a7bbd99c5f1b82fc4e370","tid":85490,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislik